'''Milo''' was a common first name shared by the following individuals:
*[[Milo Fourstar]], the [[Human/Legends|Human]] [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] operative on [[Arbra/Legends|Arbra]];
*[[Milo Mensix]], the [[Mustafarian/Legends|Mustafarian]] founder of [[Mensix Corp]];
*[[Milo Phineas]], the [[Imperial Navy/Legends|Imperial Navy]] [[Captain/Legends|Captain]];
*[[Milo Strander]], [[Stormtrooper/Legends|Stormtrooper]];
*[[Milo Thirk]], the Bureau Chief for [[Alliance Intelligence/Legends|Alliance Intelligence]] in the [[Bespin system/Legends|Bespin system]].

